node.text:
@lunamadecreations will be hosting their next Live Sale Tuesday August 17, at 8:30pm EST!! 
New arrivals have been added to their shop in limited quantities and they are happy for you guys to see what they have! From mats to pens to crystals of course! Swipe for a sneak peek 👀
